-- State Street’s Powers Seeks to Expand Active Money Management
-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   C o n d o n
-- 2012-02-09T19:04:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-09/state-street-s-powers-seeks-to-expand-active-money-management.html
Scott Powers, head of State Street
Corp.’s investments unit, said the Boston-based company is
looking to increase its active management business.  “We’re focused on broadening out our active
capabilities,” Powers said during a presentation in  New York  to
analysts. He said the company wouldn’t consider acquisitions in
passive investing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
